118
00:07:03,170 --> 00:07:03,890
No way.

119
00:07:04,570 --> 00:07:05,930
I've been a strong cultivator

120
00:07:06,170 --> 00:07:07,250
since I was a kid.

121
00:07:07,570 --> 00:07:09,130
How could I not have one?

122
00:07:09,530 --> 00:07:10,730
The spirit sword didn't react.

123
00:07:11,450 --> 00:07:12,130
Please step back.

124
00:07:12,850 --> 00:07:13,970
No reaction?

125
00:07:14,170 --> 00:07:15,690
What if the sword's wrong?

126
00:07:16,410 --> 00:07:19,090
I came all the way to seek immortality.

127
00:07:19,690 --> 00:07:21,290
Let me speak to the head

128
00:07:21,450 --> 00:07:22,370
