211
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:39,010
Master, look,

212
00:11:39,170 --> 00:11:39,730
it's glowing.

213
00:11:39,890 --> 00:11:40,970
Can I stay now?

214
00:11:42,610 --> 00:11:43,130
No.

215
00:11:43,610 --> 00:11:44,410
